title: Glasses Classification Dataset
subtitle: Dataset for image classification
description: This dataset contains a diverse range of images featuring various types, styles, and designs of eyeglasses. Its primary objective is to serve as a comprehensive resource for training and evaluating machine learning models aimed at accurately categorizing and classifying different styles and attributes of glasses depicted in images.
